%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a3bea323d7045194c8f64259af0251b6, type: 3}
  m_Name: ParisDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueTitle: Stadium Dialouge
  lines:
  - speakerName: Four Layer Booger
    text: Phew what a flight, you made it alright King?
    portrait: {fileID: 1557858435241320781, guid: 9e26393fe1f0caf4393d7094cc0d811c, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 0
  - speakerName: The King
    text: Yeah, first time im outside of Sweden, a bit too warm for my taste. Now
      who is it we're meeting Clown?
    portrait: {fileID: -5769496865783770079, guid: e55db05dbd6049a4b90ad5a20db6996d, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 0
  - speakerName: Pagliacci
    text: My friends, meet Don Giovanni. He  was present when our friends show in
      Mobile, Alabama was crashed.
    portrait: {fileID: 1868944637151657545, guid: fb2e480e1a67d4549bce9a3037146373, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Don Giovanni
    text: Hello, what Pagliacci told you is true. Was your performance also crashed
      by strange men?
    portrait: {fileID: 1441219509135777989, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: The King
    text: Thats right Mr Giovanni, you have a clue who these guys are?
    portrait: {fileID: -5769496865783770079, guid: e55db05dbd6049a4b90ad5a20db6996d, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 0
  - speakerName: Don Giovanni
    text: I am in contact with people of the performing and musical arts across the
      world. Seems these men have tried to interrupt acts wherever there is an artist
      performing, but for what end I am not certain.
    portrait: {fileID: 1441219509135777989, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Don Giovanni
    text: I was in Alabama with my troupe of performers last week visiting our friends,
      thats where we were attacked.
    portrait: {fileID: 2985656031333556012, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Don Giovanni
    text: 'It was a local show, nothing big. We fought them of with the help of local
      acts but there were too many of them, they abducted many of the performers,
      disappearing into the night. '
    portrait: {fileID: 2985656031333556012, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Don Giovanni
    text: We're only here because we managed to hide last second in a big locker
      backstage.
    portrait: {fileID: 1441219509135777989, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Don Giovanni
    text: Ever since that incident we have kept our masks on as to remain anonymous.
      You have already met pagliacci, with me as well i have the bull fighter from
      Carmen.
    portrait: {fileID: 2985656031333556012, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Don Giovanni
    text: You have already met Pagliacci, but with me as well I have the bull fighter
      from Carmen.
    portrait: {fileID: 2985656031333556012, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Toreador
    text: Hello, nice to meet you.
    portrait: {fileID: 1422787415573463666, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Don Giovanni
    text: Me and the rest of my troupe do not want to stay in hiding from these brutes.
      We wish to understand who is sending these men.
    portrait: {fileID: 1441219509135777989, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Don Giovanni
    text: We plan to gather performers of all stripes to face the next wave head
      on, maybe we can capture one of these strangers.
    portrait: {fileID: 2985656031333556012, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Toreador
    text: Hey guys, I heard a noise?
    portrait: {fileID: 1422787415573463666, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Stranger
    text: I must destroy you!
    portrait: {fileID: -3008126765985210772, guid: 14ebe5b5c1d2d9f43ae5ebe41484236c, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
  - speakerName: Don Giovanni
    text: Oh no, they must have followed us here! To arms people!
    portrait: {fileID: 2985656031333556012, guid: 8a94cabe2c209bc40a3d0ac466045a32, type: 3}
    speakerOnLeft: 1
